Pat Cummins serves this full and on off, Temba Bavuma drives it firmly through covers as Marnus Labuschagne chases and stops it. Three runs taken!
Another full delivery, on off, Marco Jansen blocks it back towards the bowler.
Pat Cummins bangs in a good bouncer, on middle, Marco Jansen ducks under it.
Back of a length and around off, Marco Jansen dabs it towards gully.
Goes fuller this time, on off at 140 clicks, Marco Jansen drives it towards mid off.
This is on a good length and on off, Temba Bavuma knocks it towards point.

A huge appeal for caught behind, but turned down. Pat Cummins has a chat with Alex Carey and goes for the review. Snicko and Hotspot shows no bat involved. Coming to the delivery, Scott Boland bowls this on a good length and around off, Temba Bavuma looks to block it but gets beaten on the outside edge. The on field decision remains and Bavuma survives. Australia lose their review.
On a length and on off, Temba Bavuma guides it with the outer half towards gully.
Fuller one and on off, Temba Bavuma drives it towards covers.
Pulls his length back a bit, on leg, Temba Bavuma clips it towards mid-wicket.
A maiden over! This is full once more and on off, Temba Bavuma drills it towards mid off.
This is on a hard length and on off, Marco Jansen keeps it out towards point. It is called no ball for overstepping.
Goes fuller this time, on off, Marco Jansen drives it through covers for a brace.
Pat Cummins bowls this on a good length and around off, Marco Jansen leaves it alone.
Back of a length and on leg, Marco Jansen gets cramped a bit and helps it towads fine leg with one hand for a single.
Short of a length and on middle, Temba Bavuma knocks it down towards the short leg region.
A bit fuller and on off, Temba Bavuma punches it towards short covers.
Full again and in the channel outside off, Temba Bavuma is happy to let it go to the keeper.
On a length and on off, Marco Jansen defends it towards covers.
Back of a length and on off, Marco Jansen pushes it towards mid off.
Fuller one and around leg, Marco Jansen tucks it towards mid-wicket.
Full again and on middle, Marco Jansen works it nicely through mid-wicket for a couple of runs.
Scott Boland bowls this on a good length and on the fifth stump line, Marco Jansen looks to block it but misses as the ball goes just past the outside edge.
This is a touch fuller and on off again, nips back in, Marco Jansen offers no shot at it.
On a length and on off, Temba Bavuma guides it towards deep backward point for a single.
Full and on off, Marco Jansen blocks it in front of covers.
This is on a good length and on off, Marco Jansen defends it towards mid off.
A good bouncer now, on middle and leg, Marco Jansen ducks underneath it.
Goes fuller and on off, Marco Jansen leans on and negotiates it towards short covers.
Pat Cummins comes around the wicket and bowls this on a hard length, on off, angling away, Marco Jansen looks to poke at it, but gets beaten all ends up.
Full and on off, Temba Bavuma blocks it towards point.
Full length, on off, blocked out.
Boland goes full, on fourth stump. Bavuma steers it to gully.
Back of a length, outside off. Temba Bavuma leaves it alone for the keeper.
This is outside off. Bavuma shoulders his arms at it.
A maiden for Bolan just his second of this innings. Fraction short, on off. Bavuma stays back and blocks it with full face.
Pat Cummins lands this short and on middle, angling away, Marco Jansen just manages to sway away from it.
This is on a good length and on middle, Marco Jansen blocks it down the pitch.
Back of a length and on off, Marco Jansen defends it towards short covers.
Full and on the pads, Marco Jansen misses his flick and the ball goes off his pads towards square leg. A leg bye is taken.
Fuller again and on off, Temba Bavuma drills it through covers for three more runs.
Pat Cummins ends the over with a sharp bouncer, on leg, Marco Jansen ducks under it.
Boland drags his length back, around fourth stump. Bavuma stands tall, opens the face and guides it towards point.
Another dot now as this length ball is blocked into the deck solidly.
Length and on off, pushed to covers.
A length ball, around off. Bavuma stays back and works it to the off side once again.
Boland fires it down leg on a fuller length. Bavuma clips it to deep square leg for a single.
Touch fuller, on fourth stump. Marco Jansen gets forward and blocks it out.
Floated, short and on off, turning in, Temba Bavuma stays back and knocks it towards silly point.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Temba Bavuma leans on and blocks it out towards the bowler.
Shorter and on off, Temba Bavuma hangs back and cuts it towards covers for a single.
A bit short and on middle, Marco Jansen defends it off the back foot.
Short again and on middle, Marco Jansen keeps it out to the leg side.

OUT! LBW! Nathan Lyon provides the breakthrough straightaway after coming into the attack. Australia use the review well here. Nathan Lyon pushes this quicker through the air, on off, straightens after hitting the deck, Marco Jansen looks to block it out, but plays down the wrong line and misses to get rapped around his back leg. There is a huge appeal for LBW, but turned down. Pat Cummins goes for the review, Snicko and Hotspot shows no bat involved and Ball Tracking shows three reds and Jansen has to go back to the hut. A great review by Australia and they are now four wickets away from victory.
Howout: lbw b Nathan Lyon

Commentary: Short of a length and outside off, Temba Bavuma slashes hard at it but faisl to connect.
This is on a good length and on off, Temba Bavuma guides it with the outer half towards point.
Length again and on middle, Temba Bavuma works it with the inner half towards mid-wicket.

FOUR! FIFTY FOR BAVUMA! This has been a fighting knock from him and he looked positive right from the start. Scott Boland serves this full and down the leg, Temba Bavuma tickles it towards the fine leg fence for a boundary.
Full again and on middle, shaping in, Temba Bavuma looks to push it away, but gets an inside edge onto his pads.
A single to end the over as this full delivery is worked towards mid on by Bavuma.
Temba Bavuma dances down the track and knocks this full delivery down to long on for one.
Full and outside off. Maharaj smashes it to covers.
FOUR! Nicely played! It is tossed up, around off. Keshav Maharaj drives it through mid off and gets a boundary. Great timing and a good-looking shot.
Pushed through quicker, on off, blocked out.
This is spilled down leg, left alone.
Short and on off. Maharaj goes back and blocks it to silly point.
Short one, spinning away. Bavuma cuts it to sweeper cover for one.
Goes through full and on off. Maharaj pushes it to cover for one.
Loops it up, outside off. driven to covers.
Tossed up, around off. Bavuma strokes it to sweeper cover and collects two runs.
Short, wide of off. Bavuma cuts it through point. One taken.
A loud appeal for caught behind! Smith tosses it up, outside off, it turns away a touch. Keshav Maharaj strides forward and tries to defend it out. He misses and gets beaten on the outside edge.
Full and on off. Bavuma presses forward and flicks it to the leg side.
On off, defended back to the bowler.
On off, blocked out.
Shorter, on off, turning into the batter. Bavuma goes back and nudges it to mid-wicket. One taken.
Full and outside off. Maharaj shuffles and defends it out solidly.
On leg stump. Maharaj tucks it to the leg side.
Full and on off, blocked out.
Slower through the air, full and outside off. It grips and turns away. Temba Bavuma does not chase it.
Short, outside off. Bavuma cuts it to point.
Fuller, on off, Bavuma defends it out.
Shorter, on off. Bavuma goes back and pulls it past mid on. They take two runs.
Looped up, on off. Bavuma defends it back to the bowler.
Starc comes 'round the wicket and angles a length ball into the right-hander. Maharaj hangs back and blocks it towards covers.
This is full, angled into the pads. Maharaj flicks it past short leg. It just bounces besides the fielder there.
Full length, attacking the stumps. Keshav Maharaj makes room and defends it out watchfully.
Starc bends his back hard and serves a sharp bouncer, on leg. Maharaj ducks under it.
Fraction short, around off. Keshav Maharaj punches it into covers. They take one before the fielder cuts it out.
Back of a length, on off. Bavuma pulls it to mid-wicket for two runs.
FOUR! Solid shot. It is full and on off. Keshav Maharaj drills it down the ground and gets a boundary to long off.
This is on the pads, Maharaj nudges it to short leg.
Full and on off, defended out.
This is full and on off. Maharaj tucks it to short leg.
This is pushed into covers for one.
It is full, on middle and leg. Bavuma tries to sweep it away. The ball takes the top-edge and goes towards fine leg. They take a couple.

OUT! RUN OUT! A catastrophe for South Africa! This is very poor cricket from South Africa and they are throwing their wickets away here. Mitchell Starc bowls this back of a length and on off, Keshav Maharaj punches it through covers and sets off for the run. Marnus Labuschagne from covers chase it down and collects it while the batters complete two runs. However, Keshav Maharaj calls for the third and Bavuma initially agrees but sends him back when he is almost near the bowler's end. Marnus Labuschagne throws it towards the bowler's end where Mitchell Starc collects it and hits bullseye at the batter's end to catch Maharaj short of his crease. The replay confirms it too. South Africa seven down now!
Howout: run out (Marnus Labuschagne / Mitchell Starc)

Commentary: Outside off, left alone.
Once again Starc serves it outside off. Rabada has no shot to offer.
A sharp bouncer, on off. Rabada ducks under it.
On a good length, wide of off. Too wide to bother Rabada though.
Kagiso Rabada swivels on his back foot and pulls this short ball off his hips towards fine leg. They get a single as there is protection in the deep.
It is full and on off. Rabada blocks it out watchfully.
A single now as this is clipped into the leg side.

OUT! CAUGHT! Nathan Lyon gets his second wicket and gets rid of a set batter in Temba Bavuma. It is tossed up, around off, turning away a hint. Temba Bavuma gets down on one knee and goes for the slog sweep. He does not connect well though. The ball lobs high in the air towards the right of mid on. Marcus Harris, the substitute fielder settels under it and takes a solid catch.
Howout: c sub Marcus Harris b Nathan Lyon

Commentary: On leg, clipped to short leg.
Anrich Nortje blocks this full dellvery to covers.
Short and outside off. Anrich Nortje cuts it to the off side.
Starc goes full and on off. Kagiso Rabada tries to clip it away but takes a blow on his pads.
Kagiso Rabada blocks this length ball watchfully.
On a good length, outside off. Rabada stands tall and punches it through covers for a single.
A bouncer now, going down leg. Anrich Nortje leaves it alone.
Swing and a miss! A good-length ball, outside off. Anrich Nortje stays back and looks to chase it but misses.
Starc serves it on a length, outside off. Anrich Nortje has no shot to offer.
This is full and on middle, coming in with the arm. Kagiso Rabada blocks it on his front foot.

OUT! CAUGHT! Kagiso Rabada holes out now. South Africa lose their ninth wicket. It is tossed up, full and on off. Kagiso Rabada gets low and goes for the sweep. He though gets a top-edge on it. The ball lobs towards mid on. Pat Cummins back-pedals and takes a sharp catch behind his head as he tumbles on the floor.
Howout: c Pat Cummins b Nathan Lyon

Commentary: Tossed up, short and on middle, turning in, Lungi Ngidi looks to block it out, but misses as the ball loops up off his pads towards short leg. There is an appeal for the catch but turned down.
Floated, full and on off, Lungi Ngidi blocks it out.
On off, kept out.
Flighted, full and off, Lungi Ngidi leans on and defends it to the off side.
Mitchell Starc bangs in a bouncer, on leg, Anrich Nortje ducks under it.
This is on a hard length and on middle, angling in, Anrich Nortje gets cramped a bit but forces it towards long on for a single.
Another fiery bouncer from Starc, on leg, Lungi Ngidi ducks under it again.
Short again and on leg, angling in, Lungi Ngidi manages to duck under it.
Mitchell Starc nails the yorker, on leg, angling away, Lungi Ngidi looks to play at it, but misses and gets hit on the pads as he almost loses his balance.
FOUR! Nice shot! This is a low full toss, on middle, Lungi Ngidi drives it straight down the ground for a boundary.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Anrich Nortje reverse sweeps it towards short third man.
Floated, full and on middle, Anrich Nortje uses his feet and whips it towards deep mid-wicket for a single.
Flighted, full and on off, Lungi Ngidi lofts it over mid off for a brace.
Quciker one, short and on middle, turning in, Lungi Ngidi is through his shot early and misses to get hit on the pads.
SIX! BANG! Lungi Ngidi goes big! This is tossed up, full and on middle, Lungi Ngidi slog-sweeps it over the deep mid-wicket fence for a biggie.
Looped up, short and off, Lungi Ngidi blocks it out.
Full and on off, angling in, Anrich Nortje drives it towards covers for a single.
Mitchell Starc bangs in a bouncer, on off this time, Lungi Ngidi ducks under it.
Short of a length and around off, Lungi Ngidi goes on his knees and lets it go to the keeper.
Back of a length and on leg, angling in, Lungi Ngidi gets cramped and mistimes his pull shot towards square leg for a run.
Mitchell Starc serves a fiery bouncer, on leg, Anrich Nortje tries to duck under it and manages to do it but falls over in the process as well.
EDGED AND FOUR! This is on a hard length and on leg, angling in, Anrich Nortje looks to block it out but gets an top edge over the keeper's head for a boundary.
Floated, full and on off, Lungi Ngidi blocks it out.
FOUR! In the gap! This is tossed up, full and on middle, Lungi Ngidi heaves it towards the wide long on fence splitting the two deep fielders for a boundary.
Flatter, full and on middle, Lungi Ngidi sweeps it towards deep mid-wicket for a single.
Flighted, full and on off, Anrich Nortje reverse sweeps it towards short third man.
Gives this one some air, on middle, Anrich Nortje uses his feet and works it of the inner half towards mid-wicket.
Another dot as this full delivery is reverse swept towards short third man again.
Tossed up, full and on off, Lungi Ngidi drives it towards long off for a single.
DROPPED! This is floated, full and on middle, Anrich Nortje looks to cut it but gets na outside edge towards slip where David Warner spills it out.

Flatter, full and on off, Anrich Nortje reverse sweeps it uppishly but just past the slip as Warner dives to his left. The batters get a run as Warner picks up and throws towards the keeper where Alex Carey misses it and the ball hits Marnus Labuschagne at short leg.
Flighted, full and on off, Lungi Ngidi leans on and blocks it out.

OUT! TIMBER! Steven Smith gets the last wicket! That is that then from this Test! It is a fitting end as a leg-spinner finishes the game for Australia. Smith loops this up above the eye-line of the batter, on leg, Lungi Ngidi goes for the big heave, but plays all around it as the ball turns in from outside leg to rattle the off pole. A ball Shane Warne would have been proud of. Australian players are delighted and the handshakes are going on in the middle. Australia win by an innings and 182 runs to seal the series!
Howout: b Steven Smith
